item.title: CVE-2018-15365|2024-08-05T09:54:03.557Z -- trend%20micro -- trend%20micro%20deep%20discovery%20inspector
item.description: A Reflected Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) vulnerability in Trend Micro Deep Discovery Inspector 3.85 and below could allow an attacker to bypass CSRF protection and conduct an attack on vulnerable installations. An attacker must be an authenticated user in order to exploit the vulnerability.
